Description: Landscape with several figures standing along a river (the Nile) in the centre, looking at a baby (Moses) being picked from the river with a small boat, trees to the left, a bridge and a town in the background Etching
Curator's comments: This is third state with erased address of Simon, for other states see 1877,1013.775 and S.4048
Acquisition notes: For the history of the acquisition of the Sheepshanks collection, please see Sheepshanks.1
